

##List of useful R packages

Feel free to add as much as you want 

#IMPORTING DATA


- haven package: read and write SPSS flies
https://haven.tidyverse.org/reference/read_spss.html

- readxl package: read excel files
https://readxl.tidyverse.org/

- tabulizer package: import pdf files
https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/tabulizer/vignettes/tabulizer.html


#TIDYING AND MANIPULATING DATA

- tidyr package: cleaning data (general package from tidyverse)
https://github.com/tidyverse/tidyr


- tidyxl package: cleaning very untidy excel files (including colours and font format)
https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/tidyxl/vignettes/tidyxl.html

Blog post:
https://www.r-bloggers.com/2018/05/tidying-messy-excel-data-tidyxl/
https://rdrr.io/cran/tidyxl/f/vignettes/tidyxl.Rmd

YouTube tutorial: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1sinC7wsS5U

- staplr package: manipulating pdf in r (i.e., rotating pdf, merging pdf)
https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/staplr/staplr.pdf
